headline: REBUILDING TRUST, ENHANCING INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITIES KEY TO THAILAND'S CAPITAL MARKET GROWTH: CMDF, OLIVER WYMAN
summary: The Thailand Capital Market Development Fund (CMDF) and Oliver Wyman, a global leader in management consulting and a business of Marsh McLennan (NYSE:MMC), today unveiled their joint whitepaper Developing The Thai Capital Market Towards An International Financial Hub, which underscores Thailand's vision to position the nation as a prominent international financial center.
